{"tid":2076130,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"JYP 證實！ITZY 確定夏天回歸～","createTime":"2020-06-23T09:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T11:29:34.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"250915513e08a95df3cacd59b1737c6ba1d54372","tid":2076130,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:52:52.000Z","msg":"韓國媒體《SPOTV News》在22日報導了 ITZY 正在準備7月底回歸的消息。此後不久，經紀公司 JYP Entertainment 出面證實，表示：「沒錯，ITZY 目前正在準備回歸，確定的時間我們會在日後公佈。」，而這也是她們繼3月發行迷你二輯《IT'z ME》後，睽違5個月的新作品。<br />\n<br />\n另外，ITZY 自2019年出道以來，發表了《DALLA DALLA》、《ICY》、《Wannabe》等熱門歌曲，而《Wannabe》更在音樂節目獲得8次音樂節目的冠軍，出道曲《DALLA DALLA》的 MV 瀏覽人次更在日前突破2億次。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kpopn.com/2020/06/23/itzy-summer-comeback\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kpopn.com%2F2020%2F06%2F23%2Fitzy-summer-comeback&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JXlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=51c91c4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kpopn.com/2020/06/23/itzy-summer-comeback</a>"},{"pid":"1b9107d9421b3a3df4650a0b3ba873776bf590f9","tid":2076130,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:53:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://epop.my/cms/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/20200609jyp9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepop.my%2Fcms%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F20200609jyp9.gif&h=f54e52c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDaddy<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ead2f1210a1a36e8cbd471f6840059d738bddb","tid":2076130,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/5fabb1f28e35463abefa006ddbbcd78f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp1.pstatp.com%2Flarge%2Fpgc-image%2F5fabb1f28e35463abefa006ddbbcd78f&h=46228025&s